{"tid":353940,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉貼) 請問簡卓峰何時會道歉？","createTime":"2017-08-10T04:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T13:14:47.000Z","uid":70194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"408333d5bc073cf4028fa714d4d56419c89d3eda","tid":353940,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人曾經係簡卓峰既受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://forum.hkej.com/node/143847-%E8%AB%8B%E5%95%8F%E7%B0%A1%E5%8D%93%E5%B3%B0%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E6%9C%83%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkej.com%2Fnode%2F143847-%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%2595%258F%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589%25EF%25BC%259F&d=z%2FT0cVt%2BJsczYFWQSvdWqMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d0605722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkej.com/node/143847-%E8%AB%8B%E5%95%8F%E7%B0%A1%E5%8D%93%E5%B3%B0%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E6%9C%83%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%EF%BC%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問簡卓峰何時會道歉？<br />\n2017年08月10日 12:03 (其他)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n1153<br />\n簡卓峰先生在2016-08-18的信報發表題目為：道指升軌失守 恒指黃昏之星2浪見頂。<br />\n <br />\n文中寫道:現在，標指又創新高，形成更大的喇叭形頂， 9RSI及MACD又頂背馳，MACD熊差距，預料蓄勢大跌逾50%，反映港股絕非牛市已重臨，但如果港股日後出現牛市，本欄會認錯及致歉。<br />\n <br />\n由當天至今天，簡生也持續看淡，我想請問，簡生何時會道歉？<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n以下是簡生一年來發表的文章題目：<br />\n <br />\n2016-10-05<br />\n恒指9月射擊之星 長和似形成頭肩頂<br />\n <br />\n2016-10-20<br />\n恒指中行日經似大小頭肩頂<br />\n <br />\n2016-11-14<br />\n恒指頭肩頂（3）浪尋底<br />\n <br />\n2017-02-28<br />\n道指11連升覓頂 匯控失守升軌尋底<br />\n <br />\n2017-03-28<br />\n道指七連跌 港股雙頭告急<br />\n <br />\n2017-06-19<br />\n恒指2浪後抽完成 展開3浪跌市<br />\n <br />\n2017-07-05<br />\n港股10年一災 7月黃昏之星啟動<br />\n <br />\n2017-07-10<br />\n恒指2浪見頂  3浪尋底至明秋"},{"pid":"71281e1e50d61ad69f8efc0a9f8dc39753acdbbd","tid":353940,"uid":90419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"你識唔識嫁！<br />\nquote一年咁撚少<br />\n我幾年前玩人地已經睇淡啦！"},{"pid":"6da0629188404ae6398ee9e21b5af01c753420e6","tid":353940,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你識唔識嫁！<br />\nquote一年咁撚少<br />\n我幾年前玩人地已經睇淡啦！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係信報見到. 老老豆豆, 我係三年前開始信佢, 開頭都有D錢執, 因為佢有時都會話係牛市 / 強勢.  後尾... 巴打你都好清楚.  <br />\n<br />\n我正式對佢既文章得啖笑係<span style=\"color: red;\">舊年8月既時候</span>... 當脫歐冇料到之後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46baf0a94d2a64e9a9f731ebd1ff38321dacda8c","tid":353940,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848580c673ff83ef0f00e6ae9bfcd5491e9578e0","tid":353940,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"點解咁多年都仲生存到"},{"pid":"147ba273fce13e43d5a858b340775bfefb541699","tid":353940,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"仲要開班聲稱好快爆晒... 仲要叫自己大師"},{"pid":"596ee7040292367d0989fdeecf6d416cab0332e9","tid":353940,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解咁多年都仲生存到</blockquote><br />\n你都去信報投稿<br />\n日日唱升"},{"pid":"e679112233c727c4b1558af55b2e00dff7755ece","tid":353940,"uid":38305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:14:47.000Z","msg":"簡sir又中"}]}